                     <interp inst="t18210110-55-off316" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18210110-55-cd317" type="crimeDate">16th of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18210110-55-off316 t18210110-55-cd317"></join>, one coat, value 10 s.; one pair of breeches, value 3 s.; one pair of drawers, value 18 d.; one writing case, value 1 s., and one pair of gloves, value 6 d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18210110-55-victim619" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
                     Dent
                  <interp inst="t18210110-55-victim619" type="surname" value="Dent"></interp>
